<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password for Tradeboard</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Reset Your Tradeboard Password</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        <p>You have requested to reset your password for Tradeboard. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to
            complete the password reset process:</p>
        <div class="otp">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 10 minutes. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email and
            ensure your account is secure.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2025 Tradeboard. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>